[https://forum.openwrt.org/viewtopic.php?pid=149441 On the OpenWrt forums] The default SSID is probably (it is the format shown in the manual) '''Aztech_XXXXXX''' where '''XXXXXX''' is the last six hex digits of the wireless interface MAC address.
